  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[On Play] If there are 5 or more cards with [Myotismon]
    in their names in your trash, delete 1 of your opponent''s unsuspended Digimon
    and trash the top card of your opponent''s security stack.[When Digivolving]
    Trash the top 5 cards of your deck. Then, if there''s a card with [Myotismon]
    in its name in your trash, gain 1 memory.'
